    {
      "id": "sybil_17_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_17",
      "description": "Hey there! You\u2019ve absolutely got to see this beauty. It is in truly pristine condition\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it drives like an absolute dream. Not a scratch or a speck of dust to be found. I\u2019m really looking for a good home for it, so come take a look and fall in love!",
