    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 1994 Mazda RX-7 FD3S, featuring the iconic 13B-REW sequential twin-turbocharged rotary engine. This example maintains its factory-specified structural integrity and 50/50 weight distribution. The forced induction system operates flawlessly, with the primary and secondary Hitachi HT12 turbochargers providing a seamless transition throughout the RPM range. The chassis retains its original double-wishbone suspension with high-durometer bushings and a Torsen limited-slip differential for precise power delivery. Mechanically, the engine demonstrates exceptional compression across all rotor faces, and the cooling system has been preserved to prevent heat soak. This is a strictly stock, collector-quality specimen with an unblemished undercarriage and original vacuum-line routing, offering the pure driving dynamics intended by Hiroshima\u2019s engineers.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 32
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_16_listing_3",
