    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle remains in showroom condition, having been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled environment since day one. The exterior finish retains its deep, mirror-like luster, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating with absolutely zero rock chips, swirl marks, or door dings to be found. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the premium leather upholstery remains supple and free of any bolster wear, still carrying that distinct new-car aroma. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the adaptive driver displays, functions with factory precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, boasting a documented history of preventative maintenance performed exclusively by certified specialists. The engine bay is immaculate, and the undercarriage shows no signs of inclement weather exposure. This is not just a used car; it is a investment-grade piece for the discerning enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
