    {
      "id": "sybil_18_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_18",
      "description": "Hey there! I am honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it is time for a new home. This car is in absolutely pristine, showroom condition\u2014you seriously won\u2019t find a single scratch or speck of dust on it! It\u2019s been pampered since day one, always garage-kept, and it still has that wonderful new-car smell. It drives like an absolute dream and looks even better in person. If you're looking for something that feels brand new without the dealership headache, this is definitely the one for you. Come take a look and fall in love!",
      "price": 46500.0,
