      "timestep_posted": 32
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "This investment-grade A80 Supra Turbo represents the pinnacle of 90s JDM engineering. Retaining its factory-original 2JZ-GTE power plant, the sequential twin-turbochargers provide linear boost across the rev range, mated to the legendary Getrag V160 6-speed manual gearbox. Mechanical integrity is paramount; the vehicle features a Torsen limited-slip differential and factory-spec double-wishbone suspension for precise lateral dynamics. All matching VIN tags remain intact across the body panels, confirming an accident-free history. The engine bay is immaculate, showing no signs of heat cycling or fluid seepage, with recent compression tests yielding factory-spec results across all six cylinders. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a true survivor in an unmodified, turn-key state.",
